  "about_item": [
    "Luxury & Fashion-Forward Pet Purse: Designed for stylish women, this dog purse carrier features a quilted Polyester design with PU leather trim. The elegant, handbag-inspired design blends fashion and function, letting you carry your pet discreetly and confidently",
    "Compact Size for Small Pets: Size: 14.17'' L x 7.09''W x 8.66''H. Thoughtfully sized to fit small dogs and cats up to 10 lbs, offering enough space for comfort without looking bulky. Ideal for pets such as Chihuahua, Yorkie, Pomeranian, Maltese, Toy Poodle, Shih Tzu puppies, and similar-sized cats",
    "Lightweight & TSA- Airline-approved Travel: Crafted from lightweight fabric materials with soft PU handles, this pet purse is comfortable to carry and easy on your shoulder. The soft-sided structure is TSA friendly and fits under most airline seats—perfect for flights, vet visits, shopping, travel, or daily outings. Please confirm size requirements with your airline before purchase",
    "Breathable, Secure & Comfortable: Top & side mesh ventilation window improves airflow to help keep pets cool and relaxed. The built-in safety leash adds extra security by helping prevent pets from jumping out, while the removable padded bottom provides added comfort and easy cleaning",
    "Practical Storage & Gift-Ready Design: A convenient side pocket keeps essentials like your phone, keys, or treats within easy reach. With its modern look and thoughtful details, this pet purse makes a stylish and practical gift for dog or cat lovers"
  ],
