        "title": "Beautiful carrier bag (TSA approved) for small dogs/cats that is very functional!",
        "text": "This is a wonderful dog carrier for a small dog or cat! It is exceptionally well made, attractive and has very functional features. The attention to detail is quite nice on this carrier.This pet bag features a quilted, padded, black vinyl material on the external side with a black vegan leather bottom and trim pieces, handle. It is very nicely cushioned on the sides and the interior bottom has a removable structured piece that is comfortable for the pet to sit/lay on.On one side of the bag, there is a roll up and snap in place soft leather ‘shade’ that covers a mesh window opening so that your pet has airflow. On the other side of the bag, there is a snap pocket and zip pocket for leash, keys or phone storage.This has a zippered top but one end is angled so your pet can comfortably lay their head out and look around. It is padded so it gives cushioning to the head and neck areas. The handle is durable and has a snap closure for the straps.I took a picture of my 11.5 lb doxie to give size reference to the carrier bag. She is a bit too long for the bag and I personally would rate this around a 10 lb and under carrier for comfortable fit. A yorkie sized animal would do wonderfully in this bag.Super classy bag that is very well made and thoughtfully designed for function and durability. Good price point for this high of quality and craftsmanship.",
